root: ^Apologies for the lack of detail upon arrival, Employee 401 does not have the clearance to hear it.
^You don’t say. So tell me, what exactly was I hired to do?
^The lack of employees means SEA.E.O wants secrecy of this place.
^Indeed! This station houses top-secret research but has served it’s purpose, and is currently being shut down.
^Your proven loyalty to the company meant you were hired! Please review the research and upload to me what is useful.
^There are also samples that need to be delivered to the surface. You must choose what those are.
